lines: Are these really the only choices I have?
I mean I like beefy, but why is that the only option?
I'm gonna be the most beautiful boy on the block.
Every girl's crazy bout a sharp dressed man.
This makes me feel like Soldier 69.
Surely THIS is how to be beautiful.
Will this make me feel good about myself?
Is this the ONLY way to be a man?
Make me a beautiful boy please!
